article_title: WATCH: Is Obamacare Really a Job Killer? [Fiore Cartoon]
article_text: Mark Fiore is a Pulitzer Prize-winning editorial cartoonist and animator whose work has appeared in the Washington Post, the Los Angeles Times, the San Francisco Examiner, and dozens of other publications. He is an active member of the American Association of Editorial Cartoonists, and has a website featuring his work.

og.description: Conservatives say that once people sign up for health insurance they'll no longer want to work. Is that really the case?
